{"tid":451012,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"請教如何有效整理通訊錄","createTime":"2017-10-28T17:07:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-30T10:49:10.000Z","uid":28203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"67105af7a215f8067257d95339e91043287a59e5","tid":451012,"uid":28203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T17:07:44.000Z","msg":"大家好，小弟使用google 嘅gmail嚟做通訊錄多年，由中學讀到大學，都唔覺得有咩問題。但而家出嚟做野，要接觸多好多嘅人，好容易有相同人名嘅情況出現，例如Alex, Calvin, Jessica, Kelly，當我用iphone搵人嘅時候，睇到同名嘅都唔知邊個先係我要搵嘅人，有時撳埋入去都分唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以想問下大家有冇咩方法可以好好咁整理好個通訊錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我對通訊錄嘅要求要有：<br />\n<br />\n可以show到公司/party, Email <br />\n可以分到工作需要同daily life嘅朋友親友<br />\n<br />\n同埋想問下，ios係咪冇得用gmail嘅group?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望大家喺software/app/system方面比較下各種contact list（gmail, iCloud, outlook, etc.)嘅優劣，同時都探討下management method，例如點入資料同分類可以方便d<br />\n<br />\nThank you<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acfabbdf8fdef5bf687261da991ee4ae0847d0d9","tid":451012,"uid":145959,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T17:11:21.000Z","msg":"Set名前面加個公司名<br />\n(CSL) Mary<br />\n(公廁)Mary<br />\n(公廁)詩雅<br />\n(歌手)詩雅<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3022db7f2604aefffcf4a9512b9f6790a4f96300","tid":451012,"uid":28203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T17:16:28.000Z","msg":"我自己公司都已經有好多人同名<br />\n<br />\n我周圍都3個Anthony"},{"pid":"b6e9773082d528bdc0279368be1584d664fd9799","tid":451012,"uid":14566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T17:23:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我自己公司都已經有好多人同名<br />\n<br />\n我周圍都3個Anthony</blockquote><br />\n入部門/入埋姓"},{"pid":"dbc46388485380ff7ab42977c0e26986c3dedc07","tid":451012,"uid":145959,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T17:23:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我自己公司都已經有好多人同名<br />\n<br />\n我周圍都3個Anthony</blockquote><br />\n(CSL IT) TONY<br />\n(CSL 摟屌)TONY"},{"pid":"a853a02622ce2d02eb4240f5030fb2875f3ce1a6","tid":451012,"uid":28203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T17:41:23.000Z","msg":"因為我用緊iPhone,開新contact嘅時候係有得入first name, last name同company，所以我唔希望係first name到打公司/部門名<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/29/013023_9b1c22fd2db3fec1714dc807792f8644.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F29%2F013023_9b1c22fd2db3fec1714dc807792f8644.jpg&h=80dedf17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係另一個問題就係我打左公司資料，contact list 都係唔會show 出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/29/013632_108a80e40afeaebd5f400239ccad500d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F29%2F013632_108a80e40afeaebd5f400239ccad500d.jpg&h=b70b4593&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/29/014122_6ce179bfdfe9e3b707638d6cc8f41a28.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F29%2F014122_6ce179bfdfe9e3b707638d6cc8f41a28.jpg&h=36e0a804&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"53a471c90e96043e227f2b4b879a9a78d2fd8d69","tid":451012,"uid":28203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T02:07:41.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e512881b2f2b152efc0b7433843b5722c74f03ef","tid":451012,"uid":28203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T06:27:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"54d840db53fe28bc6ec5ce24861db178139e1a3f","tid":451012,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T14:51:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我自己公司都已經有好多人同名<br />\n<br />\n我周圍都3個Anthony</blockquote>